&gt;     for (int i = headerLen; i &lt; datagramPacket.getLength(); i++){
&gt;         data[i - headerLen] = datagramPacket.getData()[i];
&gt;     }

This code assume that what it receives over the network is a 16-byte pcap header followed by the packet data.

However, your server is *not* sending the pcap header, it&#39;s *only* sending the packet data, so this won&#39;t work.

